= Interviews with Tony Klein and Dave Grundy

URL = http://www.radio4all.net/index.php/program/32035


=Description=

"A Vermont-centric program this week: House Natural Resources and Energy Committee chair Tony Klein explains why he wants Entergy Corporation to start paying into the Vermont Yankee Decommissioning Fund. And East Montpelier Energy Committee chair Dave Grundy is the local coordinator for the neighbor-helping-neighbor pilot program Vermont Community Energy Mobilization Project."


